<ITEM>Bobak de&s;cribed, vii. 198.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Bona&s;us, vii. 150. The &s;ame with the bi&s;on of the Latins, 168.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Bonavi&s;ta: An incredible number of goats on that i&s;land, iii. 493.</ITEM>
